cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with data fusion methods for multi-view data classification, specifically in the context of mammography images for breast microcalcification classification. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Neural networks are used in the implementation, so neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) is also a possible category. Finally, information retrieval (cs.IR) could be relevant as the paper deals with combining information from multiple sources.
